<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-37-0560 </DOCNO><TEXT>From the Engineering Biology Department of Sofia University's microbiologicalcollection a Trichoderma species mutant strain was found to be most promisingon preparation of cellulase enzymic products. Based on solid-phase andsubmerged cultures laboratory and industrial scale procedures for obtainingcellulase products were developed. Different enzyme application possibilitieswere investigated and the results were presented.</TEXT></DOC>